      "text": "<p>Trebalo bi da kreirate novi <code>div</code> unutar vašeg elementa <code>body</code>.</p>",
      "testString": "const divs = [...document.querySelector('body')?.children].filter(child => child?.localName === 'div');\r\nassert(divs?.length === 1);"
